kolka cool is a latvian film . this is a film that depicts the mentality of the inhabitants of a small village on the baltic coast .   three guys are trying to fulfill their lives by drinking beer , killing time and picking fights with neighboring villagers .   the main character , andzha , is trying to convince his girlfriend to marry him .   the sudden arrival of his elder brother guido starts a series of events where elevated self-esteem , pride and cravings for love that is stronger than death emerge as the dominant themes .   iveta pole won the lielais kristaps award for best actress in 2012 for her performance in the film .